## UI Design
- Floating panel at top of editor (similar to VS Code/browser find)
- Blur backdrop, rounded corners, shadow
- Matches Stone's design tokens (--background, --border, --primary)
- Highlighted matches use --primary color with low opacity

## Keyboard Shortcuts
- `Cmd+F` / `Ctrl+F` - Open find/replace
- `Escape` - Close
- `Enter` - Find next
- `Shift+Enter` - Find previous
- `Cmd+Enter` - Replace current
- `Cmd+Shift+Enter` - Replace all
